; Coverage test for xact.cc lines 319-470
; Tests LIFO lot matching in finalize().  Exercises:
;   - lot_matching_policy == lifo (line 409-411)
;   - LIFO sort order (newest lot consumed first)
;   - splitting a sale across two lots

2024/01/01 Buy Lot 1
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$150.00} [2024/01/01]
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/01 Buy Lot 2
    Assets:Brokerage    5 AAPL {$160.00} [2024/02/01]
    Assets:Cash

2024/03/01 Sell LIFO
    Assets:Brokerage    -7 AAPL @ $170.00
    Assets:Cash

test --lot-matching lifo reg Assets:Brokerage
24-Jan-01 Buy Lot 1             Assets:Brokerage             5 AAPL       5 AAPL
24-Feb-01 Buy Lot 2             Assets:Brokerage             5 AAPL      10 AAPL
24-Mar-01 Sell LIFO             Assets:Brokerage            -5 AAPL       5 AAPL
                                Assets:Brokerage            -2 AAPL       3 AAPL
end test
